          <mj-text color=#637381 font-size=16px> We hope you enjoy the second edition of our weekly newsletter! Keep an eye out for an email with more instructions on how you can help contribute to <i>The Record.</i> <br><br> - <i>The Record Editorial Board</i> </mj-text>
