          <mj-text color=#212b35 font-weight=bold font-size=20px> Artist of the Issue: Dom Bellido ’20 </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#212b35 font-size=12px height=15px font-weight=bold> Yihan Ding ’22 and Stephanie Ge ’22, Arts Editors </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#637381 font-size=16px> The ink. board will hold a virtual poetry reading in Chapel on Thursday, April 23. The Arts Editors interviewed Dom Bellido ’20, one of the board members of ink, about his experience with poetry and creative writing. This interview has been
