      <!-- Start of text -->
      <mj-section background-color=#ffffff padding-left=15px padding-right=15px>
        <mj-column width=100%>
          <mj-text color=#637381 font-size=12px align=right padding-right=5px> <i></i> </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#212b35 font-weight=bold font-size=20px> Help Us Help You </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#212b35 font-size=12px height=15px font-weight=bold> The CXXII Executive Board </mj-text>
          <mj-text color=#637381 font-size=16px> The Record is a community effort. It is not just our large editorial board that helps produce every weekly issue—there are many more people involved. To give you an idea, we reach out to nearly 50 people for every eight-page issue. Without realizing
